show.description: RETURN OF THE SUPREME - Hero's fortunes change when his four formidable aunts—an Esteemed Guardian, a top movie star, a miracle doctor, and a business mogul—locate him. With their unwavering support, He embarks on a journey to reclaim his identity and rightful place, confronting the impostor who usurped his position and seeking justice for the wrongs he suffered.
